snippet.title: Super Mystery Wars - Episode Phoenix/Episode Conan Trailer
snippet.description:
This is an extended trailer for two Ace Attorney fan-cases with crossovers from Mystery stories such as Umineko, Detective Conan, Nougami Neuro, Persona 5, Milky Holmes, and more.

The first chapter, Episode Phoenix: The Poisonous Tournabout was created for a fan case competition, and Episode Conan is set in the same continuity, with both leading up to the same upcoming story from different perspectives.

I claim no ownership over any of the characters or other intellectual property contained within, and no affiliation with the owners thereof, and this project is purely non-profit.
